verbose_text: The comparison between the two groups showed that there were no significant differences with some glycemic parameters containing FPG and HbA1c (P> 0.05), but there were significant differences in insulin levels and HOMA-IR which were calculated based on the power of 80% and alpha = 5% (16.6 +/- 5.9; 3.7 +/- 1.5, resp.
